OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCan mind-controlled VR     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fgames help stroke patients?
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A system which can translate human     
OL,6, brain activity into actions without any
OL,7, physical movement is being developed by
OL,8, a neurotech firm called Cogitat.       
OL,10,FWhen wearing a prototype headset, basic
OL,11,Factions in virtual reality can be      
OL,12,Fcarried out by thinking about them.    
OL,14,FSo for example, in a game where a VR   
OL,15,Fjet ski is controlled by handles, you  
OL,16,Fmove by thinking about it, rather than 
OL,17,Fsqueezing your hands.                  
OL,19,FElon Musk's firm Neuralink is          
OL,20,Fdeveloping a similar concept.          
